!! Opening the Agent Workspace

Click the "Agent" icon (`workspace-agent`) in the left sidebar to enter the agent workspace.

!! Starting a Conversation

# Click the "+" new tab button at the top
# Select an agent from the search box (e.g. "Default Agent"), or type a question directly
# Type your question in the input box at the bottom and press Enter

Agents automatically use built-in tools to handle complex tasks:

* `wiki-search`: Search tiddlers in the workspace using a TiddlyWiki filter
* `wiki-operation`: Create or modify tiddlers in the workspace

!! Managing Tabs

* Each conversation opens as a new tab; the title is auto-generated by the AI and can be edited
* Right-click a tab to pin frequently used conversations
* Click the search button at the top to find past conversations, recently closed tabs, and history

!! Conversation Toolbar (left to right)

* Title (editable)
* Model selector: switch the AI endpoint for this conversation
* Agent settings: adjust the prompt for this conversation only
* Prompt preview: inspect the complete prompt that will be sent to the AI
